If rcell.Value <> "" Then
    For rep = 1 To (Worksheets.Count)
     If LCase(Sheets(rep).Name) = LCase(rcell) Then
     MsgBox "This sheet already exists!"
     Exit Sub


    End If
	
Sheets("TestScript").Copy After:=Sheets(Worksheets.Count)
      Sheets(Sheets.Count).Name = rcell.Value

End If
